<br>
Why lock the zones to 80% of the population that cannot or will not spend the time necessary for entry.  <br>
<br>
Sony needs to implement some sort of non flag questable method of entry into the higher tier zones, excluding of course select zones similiar to what they did in Luclin &amp; Velious - VT and ST for example.  <br>
<br>
I don't care if the timeframe for such quests were as exhausting as raiding to get there ie it may take 6 months to complete but at least have a damn option for people who can't or will not spend 12 hours per day raiding.  <br>
<br>
And for me who just cringes to think about spending all her time with 60 egotistical fucktards gloating and drooling over their &quot;successes&quot;.<br>
<br>
Disclaimer - &quot;egotistical fucktards&quot; is not a directed attack at any particular individual or group of individuals or organizations whether living or dead or rerolled.  It refers to the &quot;uber&quot; guild.   <br>
